e. You&#8217;re right that it isn&#8217;t a very sweet though! I like my cakes plenty sweet so I&#8217;ll probably be adding a ton more next time I make it. I&#8217;m not happy that it&#8217;s so easy to make because now I can see myself eating this every day and that&#8217;s just not good for my health!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/06/the-one-chocolate-mug-cake/?replytocom=80898#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-80898\", \"80898\", \"respond\", \"13164\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-81031\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6ca93510d0ee455095347f2dfb9a223d?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\">TruthMcBane</cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2012/06/the-one-chocolate-mug-cake/#comment-81031\">06.03.13 at 7:22 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>As written, this recipe is inedible. It *needs* more sugar or chocolate chips. I can still taste the vegetable oil.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/06/the-one-chocolate-mug-cake/?replytocom=81031#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-81031\", \"81031\", \"respond\", \"13164\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"comment-81772\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.c